I enjoy creating real-time hardware projects such as traffic control systems, gesture-based switches, and automation tools using Arduino, ARM, STM32, and ESP32.

My engineering focus areas include:
- Embedded C and Microcontroller Programming  
- STM32 ARM Cortex development  
- IoT communication (LoRa, MQTT, BLE, Wi-Fi)  
